{"tid":1403710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔係回帶] 美國發生槍擊事件，超過二十名死者","createTime":"2019-08-03T21:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T21:19:16.000Z","uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5ed9d729c541c0019cd59d47676f7f7500254248","tid":1403710,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:04:35.000Z","msg":"&bull;El Paso mayor's office confirms multiple fatalities in a mass-shooting inside a local Walmart on Saturday <br />\n&bull;Texas Lt. Governor Dan Patrick says the suspect, a 21-year-old male, has been taken into custody alive<br />\n&bull;The shooting took place at the Walmart near the Cielo Vista Mall in El Paso, Texas on Saturday<br />\n&bull;A local NBC affiliate is reporting that at least 18 people were killed and nearly two dozen were wounded<br />\n&bull;A number of local businesses, shops, and restaurants were in lock down during the shooting<br />\n&bull;Witnesses posted video on social media showing panicked shoppers fleeing during the shooting <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/08/03/21/16854016-7317905-Panicked_shoppers_flee_the_Cielo_Vista_Mall_in_El_Paso_on_Saturd-a-61_1564864284856.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2F21%2F16854016-7317905-Panicked_shoppers_flee_the_Cielo_Vista_Mall_in_El_Paso_on_Saturd-a-61_1564864284856.jpg&h=08b0c31b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Panicked shoppers flee the Cielo Vista Mall in El Paso on Saturday after a gunman opened fire inside a nearby Walmart<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/08/03/21/16854014-7317905-Local_reports_indicate_that_at_least_22_people_were_killed_in_th-a-62_1564864284857.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2F21%2F16854014-7317905-Local_reports_indicate_that_at_least_22_people_were_killed_in_th-a-62_1564864284857.jpg&h=8deec766&s={SIZE}\" /