Active_Shooting_Stay_away_from_Cielo_Vista_Mall_Area_Scene_is_S-a-91_1564864332246.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2F21%2F16851568-7317905-_Active_Shooting_Stay_away_from_Cielo_Vista_Mall_Area_Scene_is_S-a-91_1564864332246.jpg&h=ad166c1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 'Active Shooting Stay away from Cielo Vista Mall Area. Scene is Still Active,' the police department tweeted on Saturday<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/08/03/21/16852284-7317905-Later_on_Saturday_El_Paso_police_said_there_were_multiple_report-a-92_1564864335141.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2F21%2F16852284-7317905-Later_on_Saturday_El_Paso_police_said_there_were_multiple_report-a-92_1564864335141.jpg&h=0d64d585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Later on Saturday, El Paso police said there were 'multiple reports of multiple shooters'"},{"pid":"d24fcb41c93492dc3742f2969726b0105d691805","tid":1403710,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/08/03/21/16851572-7317905-Earlier_on_Saturday_the_police_tweeted_Active_Shooter_in_area_of-a-93_1564864338803.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2F21%2F16851572-7317905-Earlier_on_Saturday_the_police_tweeted_Active_Shooter_in_area_of-a-93_1564864338803.jpg&h=b64fb7df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Earlier on Saturday, the police tweeted: 'Active Shooter in area of Hawkins and Gateway East.' Hawkins and Gateway are two streets that flank the Walmart. El Paso police later confirmed that the active shooter was inside a Walmart<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/08/03/21/16851850-7317905-Beto_O_Rourke_the_Democratic_presidential_candidate_and_former_U-a-94_1564864342896.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2F21%2F16851850-7317905-Beto_O_Rourke_the_Democratic_presidential_candidate_and_former_U-a-94_1564864342896.jpg&h=04f5b052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Beto O'Rourke, the Democratic presidential candidate and former U.S. congressman who represented El Paso, tweeted: 'Truly heartbreaking. Stay safe, El Paso'<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/08/03/21/16852814-7317905-O_Rourke_s_successor_House_Rep_Veronica_Escobar_tweeted_Utterly_-a-95_1564864346030.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2F21%2F16852814-7317905-O_Rourke_s_successor_House_Rep_Veronica_Escobar_tweeted_Utterly_-a-95_1564864346030.jpg&h=bb556a75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n O'Rourke's successor, House Rep. Veronica Escobar, tweeted: 'Utterly heartbroken by the developing news in El Paso. Monitoring the situation and in communication with our law enforcement. Please stay safe.'<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/08/03/21/16852812-7317905-Texas_Governor_Greg_Abbott_tweeted_In_El_Paso_the_Texas_Dept_of_-a-96_1564864349183.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2F21%2F16852812-7317905-Texas_Governor_Greg_Abbott_tweeted_In_El_Paso_the_Texas_Dept_of_-a-96_1564864349183.jpg&h=d7209ced&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Texas Governor Greg Abbott tweeted: 'In El Paso, the Texas Dept. of Public Safety is assisting local law enforcement &amp; federal authorities to bring this tragedy to the swiftest &amp; safest possible conclusion.'<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/08/03/21/16854604-7317905-Trump_tweeted_Terrible_shootings_in_ElPaso_Texas_Reports_are_ver-a-97_1564864352031.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2F21%2F16854604-7317905-Trump_tweeted_Terrible_shootings_in_ElPaso_Texas_Reports_are_ver-a-97_1564864352031.jpg&h=55bdc54b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Trump tweeted: 'Terrible shootings in ElPaso, Texas. Reports are very bad, many killed. Working with State and Local authorities, and Law Enforcement.'<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/08/03/21/16852270-7317905-The_Bureau_of_Alcohol_Tobacco_Firearms_and_Explosives_announced_-a-98_1564864370988.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2F21%2F16852270-7317905-The_Bureau_of_Alcohol_Tobacco_Firearms_and_Explosives_announced_-a-98_1564864370988.jpg&h=f2231b84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The Bureau of Alcohol, Tobacco, Firearms, and Explosives announced that it has dispatched federal agents to the scene to assist local law enforcement<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/08/03/21/16852738-7317905-image-a-70_1564864284901.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2F21%2F16852738-7317905-image-a-70_1564864284901.jpg&h=cf9a06bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n El Paso is located on the border separating the United States and Mexico<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/08/03/21/16852770-7317905-Heavily_armed_police_are_seen_next_to_an_FBI_armored_vehicle_nex-a-72_1564864284941.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2F21%2F16852770-7317905-Heavily_armed_police_are_seen_next_to_an_FBI_armored_vehicle_nex-a-72_1564864284941.jpg&h=ecf92b85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Heavily armed police are seen next to an FBI armored vehicle next to the Cielo Vista Mall in El Paso on Saturday<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/08/03/21/16852798-7317905-Police_stand_at_attention_during_an_active_shooter_at_a_Walmart_-a-74_1564864285039.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2F21%2F16852